	<h1 class="title">战败 70 年后，山田洋次出了部电影来讲述长崎的故事</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/4369/small/4369.jpg?1419239008" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">晏文静 </span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2015-12-16 07:02:22 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/19127/medium/19127.png?1450172458" alt="" />			
	</div>
